Oh, dia berdiri.

161
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:52,588
Astaga./ Luar biasa.

162
00:12:52,588 --> 00:12:55,191
Aku tidak bisa membiarkanmu tenang.

163
00:12:55,291 --> 00:12:56,692
Bagus. Kau bisa memberi beberapa pukulan.

164
00:12:58,261 --> 00:13:00,196
Lawan aku.

165
00:13:00,963 --> 00:13:03,032
Kenapa hanya menatapku?

166
00:13:04,801 --> 00:13:07,670
Pukulan bagus./ Mengapa?

167
00:13:07,670 --> 00:13:10,072
Kenapa kau diam ketika dipukul?

168
00:13:10,072 --> 00:13:12,108
Sudah kubilang. Aku akan membiarkannya.

169
00:13:12,108 --> 00:13:13,409
Benar.

170
00:13:13,409 --> 00:13:14,811
Apa yang kalian lakukan?

171
00:13:18,214 --> 00:13:19,515
Sial.

172
00:13:23,653 --> 00:13:26,656
<i>Hujan, di kereta menuju selatan...</i>

173
00:13:26,656 --> 00:13:28,524
<i>...dari jalan Honam</i>./ Oh, Hyungnim.

174
00:13:29,258 --> 00:13:32,361
Ayo, lanjutkan. Baiklah, iya.

175
00:13:32,361 --> 00:13:33,529
Astaga, minggir.

176
00:13:33,529 --> 00:13:35,932
Kenapa kalian sangat senang?/ 
Bukan apa-apa.

177
00:13:35,932 --> 00:13:37,767
Kuharap kalian tidak menganggap
semua ini lucu.

178
00:13:37,767 --> 00:13:39,435
Tidak./ Tidak mungkin.

179
00:13:39,435 --> 00:13:41,304
