dia hampir meninggal.

183
00:13:49,779 --> 00:13:52,448
<i>Ikan duyung hidup dalam berkelompok,</i>

184
00:13:52,448 --> 00:13:53,516
<i>...dan habitat mereka ditentukan...</i>

185
00:13:53,516 --> 00:13:56,252
Hei!./ Apa itu?

186
00:13:56,452 --> 00:13:58,287
